'''电现象'''（electrical phenomena）是关于[[电|电]]的物理[[现象|现象]]，例如人类熟知的[[闪电|闪电]]就是[[自然界|自然界]]中的一种[[放电|放电]]现象。此外，随着[[电学|电学]]的发展，人们还认识到了[[摩擦起電效應|摩擦起电]]、[[静电感应|静电感应]]、[[电磁感应|电磁感应]]、[[壓電效應|壓電效應]]等各种电现象<ref name="electricity">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica | title = electricity | url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/182915/electricity | author = Encyclopædia Britannica Online | date =  | accessdate = 2014-04-06 | archive-date = 2014-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220154149/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/182915/electricity | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

