</ref><ref name=Williams>{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Tn4KAAAAMAAJ&dq=intitle:the+intitle:origins+intitle:of+intitle:field+intitle:theory&lr=&as_brr=0&pgis=1 |title=The Origins of Field Theory |author= L. Pearce Williams |year= 1966 |publisher=Random House |page= 77-78, 133 (for electromagnetic induction) ; p. 85-89, 133 (for electrostatic induction)}}</ref>。

1834年[[德国|德国]]物理学家[[海因里希·楞次|海因里希·楞次]]发现由於磁通量的改變而產生的[[感應電流|感應電流]]，其方向為抵抗磁通量改變的方向，被称为[[楞次定律|楞次定律]]<ref>{{cite book | author=Griffiths, David J.|title=Introduction to Electrodynamics (3rd ed.)| publisher=Prentice Hall |year=1998|pages = pp. 301-304|isbn=0-13-805326-X}}</ref>。楞次定律对[[法拉第電磁感應定律|法拉第電磁感應定律]]做了补充，指出[[電感|電感]]是當通過[[載流迴路|載流迴路]]的[[電流|電流]]发生改變時，會出現[[電動勢|電動勢]]來抵抗電流的改變。術語「電感」是1886年由[[奥利弗·赫维赛德|奥利弗·赫维赛德]]命名，分为[[自感|自感]]和[[互感|互感]]<ref>Heaviside, O. Electrician. Feb. 12, 1886, p. 271.見[http://books.google.com/books?id=bywPAAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=elecrrical+papers+heavyside 該文集的再版] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=bywPAAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=elecrrical+papers+heavyside |date=20130618130046 }}</ref>。通常自感是以字母「L」標記，是為了紀念物理學家[[海因里希·楞次|海因里希·楞次]]的貢獻<ref>{{cite web 
